I hope that this email finds you very well. I have been mulling over our paper. It is too good to go to waste and the topic continues to be timely. My attempts at submission to a CABS journal have proved unsuccessful, so I would like to try a submission to one of the journals you suggested: the Social Indicators Research Journal. This seems to have a good impact factor and a speed initial turnaround time.

I am in and out over the next couple of weeks, but would very much like to submit this before the end of the month.

What do you think?

